The archives don't seem to lead to a sure fix, but
http://www.type2.com/archive/vintagebus/050703.html has a suggestion.

This problem seems to have happened before:
http://www.type2.com/archive/vintagebus/073853.html

Pages 359 (diagram) and 363 (list) of
http://failsure.net/oacdp/5867part.html
say that there is only one cable, length 5715 mm, for all post-Barndoor
Buses.

